data.description: Back on the market, due to buyer finances. This charming 2-bedroom (possible 3rd) 1-bath home nestled on a corner lot with a single garage, a side porch, and a host of unique features that make it a perfect blend of modern comfort and rustic charm. Bedrooms have a nice closet space plus each room has its own storage closet or small closet, play area for a child. This home has a new electric panel and new water heater was just installed. The upper level has corrugated metal, while the main floor showcases the warmth of colored barn wood siding. The living room has an electric fireplace, creating a welcoming atmosphere and Vintage lights adorn the dining room, casting a warm and nostalgic glow. One of the standout features of this home is the charming barn door that leads into the kitchen and the vintage doors that lead to the outside porch, a perfect place for morning coffee. Seller is giving $500 towards a Home Warranty.
